#: ../../source/design/v0.3-trade-history-design.md:374
msgid "8.2 Method B — snapshot diff"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/design/v0.3-trade-history-design.md:376
msgid ""
"**Use case**: Anno 117 may not retain a long history of `<TradedGoods>`. "
"Method B reconstructs trade activity from periodic save snapshots "
"maintained by the user."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/design/v0.3-trade-history-design.md:378
msgid "**Algorithm**:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/design/v0.3-trade-history-design.md:380
msgid "Load snapshot `t0` and `t1`. Compute per-island per-good inventory."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/design/v0.3-trade-history-design.md:381
msgid "For each `(island, good)`, take `Δ = stock(t1) - stock(t0)`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/design/v0.3-trade-history-design.md:382
msgid ""
"Subtract known production/consumption derived from buildings (using "
"`GoodsTradeHandler.ProductGainPerArea`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/design/v0.3-trade-history-design.md:383
msgid ""
"Residual `Δ` is attributed to a synthetic `TradeEvent` with "
"`source_method=\"diff\"`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/design/v0.3-trade-history-design.md:384
msgid ""
"Match deltas across islands within the same session to infer "
"counterparties when possible."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/design/v0.3-trade-history-design.md:386
msgid "**Caveats**:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/design/v0.3-trade-history-design.md:387
msgid "Less precise than Method A (no per-event timestamp)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/design/v0.3-trade-history-design.md:388
msgid "Cannot detect short trades that net to zero between snapshots."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/design/v0.3-trade-history-design.md:389
msgid ""
"Should be presented to users with an honesty label (\"inferred from "
"snapshot delta\")."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/design/v0.3-trade-history-design.md:391
